[cmd]
$ qinAegis --help
stdout ```
Usage: qinAegis <COMMAND>

Commands:
  tui          Start interactive TUI
  setup        Setup or reconfigure QinAegis (interactive)
  init         Initialize QinAegis configuration
  project      Manage projects
  config       Show current configuration
  explore
  generate
  review       Review, approve, reject, or archive test cases
  run
  report
  export       Export project to various formats
  performance
  stress
  gate         Run quality gate checks
  help         Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
```

[cmd]
$ qinAegis --version
stdout ```
qinAegis 0.1.0
```